    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors at MRL 2. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were accepted as not-assessed per standard guidance for MRL 2 Class II devices. The discretization error GCI of 6.8% marginally exceeds the 5% acceptance criterion but was judged by the team to be within engineering tolerance given the conservative nature of the worst-case operating point selection. All other assessed factors met or exceeded required levels. The overall credibility package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
